export const FontFamily = {
    poppinsBold: "Poppins_bold",
    josefinSansMedium: "Josefin Sans_medium",
    poppinsRegular: "Poppins_regular",
    mSmall: "Lato",
    textS2Reguler: "DM Sans_regular",
    textSMedium: "DM Sans_medium",
    captionSMedium: "Plus Jakarta Sans_medium",
    captionSSemiBold: "Plus Jakarta Sans_semibold",
    textMBold: "Plus Jakarta Sans_bold",
    textMRegular: "Plus Jakarta Sans_regular",
    mButton: "Poppins_semibold",
    spaceGroteskBold: "Space Grotesk_bold",
    poppinsMedium: "Poppins_medium",
  };
  /* font sizes */
  export const FontSize = {
    size_11xl: 30,
    size_17xl: 36,
    textSMedium_size: 12,
    size_xl: 20,
    mSmall_size: 14,
    size_mini: 15,
    size_6xl: 25,
    textS2Reguler_size: 10,
    textXLSemiBold_size: 18,
    textL3Reguler_size: 16,
  };
  /* Colors */
  export const Color = {
    blackModeSecondaryDark: "#2f3c50",
    darkslategray_100: "#3b363f",
    blackModePrimaryDark: "#28333f",
    charlestonGreen: "#1f2b36",
    sUNRISEWhite: "#fff",
    darkgray_100: "#aea8b2",
    darkgray_200: "#aaa",
    neutral50: "#a9a8aa",
    darkgray_300: "rgba(174, 168, 178, 0.2)",
    neutral90: "#262329",
    neutral100: "#141316",
    gray_100: "rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8)",
    gray_200: "rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05)",
    gray_300: "rgba(255, 255, 255, 0)",
    gray_400: "rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.32)",
    gray_500: "rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.36)",
    gray_600: "rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.56)",
    gray_700: "rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8)",
    tomato: "#fb5b51",
    lightgreen: "#6aeca6",
    tuftsBlue: "#3c94e5",
    sUNRISECoral: "#7b61ff",
    neutral30: "#e4e4e4",
    gainsboro_100: "#d9d9d9",
    gainsboro_200: "rgba(217, 217, 217, 0.25)",
    neutral10: "#f6f6f6",
    whitesmoke_100: "rgba(240, 240, 240, 0.32)",
    redMain: "#f60909",
    neutral80: "#565358",
    primaryMain: "#13c782",
    mediumseagreen_100: "#07c57d",
    slategray_100: "#4b6680",
    silver_100: "#c9c9c9",
    neutral40: "#c9c8c9",
    black: "#000",
    royalblue: "#677fff",
  };
  /* Paddings */
  export const Padding = {
    p_5xs: 8,
    p_xs: 12,
    p_base: 16,
    p_13xl: 32,
    p_sm: 14,
    p_3xs: 10,
    p_xs_1: 11,
    p_lg: 18,
    p_7xs: 6,
  };
  /* border radiuses */
  export const Border = {
    br_81xl: 100,
    br_xl: 20,
    br_xs: 12,
    br_5xs: 8,
    br_9xs: 4,
    br_3xs: 10,
    br_base: 16,
    br_21xl: 40,
    br_5xl: 24,
    br_35xl: 54,
    br_7xl: 26,
    br_73xl_9: 93,
  };
